#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.172"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.172:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.172:0.2"
msgid "18. Upāsakavagga"
msgstr "18. A Lay Follower"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.172:0.3"
msgid "172. Visāradasutta"
msgstr "172. Assured"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.204"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.172:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato upāsako avisārado agāraṃ "
"ajjhāvasati."
msgstr "“A lay follower living at home with five qualities is not self-assured."

msgctxt "an5.172:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.172:1.3"
msgid "Pāṇātipātī hoti … pe … surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhāyī hoti."
msgstr ""
"They kill living creatures, steal, commit sexual misconduct, lie, and use "
"alcoholic drinks that cause negligence."

msgctxt "an5.172:1.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato upāsako avisārado agāraṃ "
"ajjhāvasati."
msgstr ""
"A lay follower living at home with these five qualities is not self-assured."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.172:2.1"
msgid ""
"Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato upāsako visārado agāraṃ ajjhāvasati."
msgstr ""
"A lay follower living at home with these five qualities is self-assured."

msgctxt "an5.172:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.172:2.3"
msgid ""
"Pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti … pe … surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā paṭivirato "
"hoti."
msgstr ""
"They don’t kill living creatures, steal, commit sexual misconduct, lie, or "
"use alcoholic drinks that cause negligence."

msgctxt "an5.172:2.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato upāsako visārado agāraṃ "
"ajjhāvasatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"A lay follower living at home with these five qualities is self-assured.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.172:2.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
